features: Package Contains: This manila file folder kit contains 6 packs of plastic file folders (9.5”x 11.5”), suitable for US letter size documents.

Premium Material: These file folders are made of high-quality polypropylene. Was tired of the paper files getting worn out and the tabs getting bent over and not staying up from reuse? These plastic files are durable, waterproof, and acid-free to protect your documents.
Manila-like Color: The color is similar to traditional manila paper, which looks totally the same but much more sturdy and more suitable for long-time use.
1/3-cut Tabs: Sizable Left/Center/Right tabs allow cascade headers from left to right for uninterrupted viewing. You could customize it with a pen, pencil or marker.

Wide Applications: These folders would help you to keep all your files organized. They are suitable for office workers, teachers and students. You can use it in any place and on any occasion, such as filing cabinets, preparing a presentation and project in school, home, office, etc.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Excellent durability but see-through
reviews.reviewText: These are really nice plastic manila-type folders. But make no mistake, they are NOT manila folders! They are for home or personal use only. The translucent plastic is not appropriate for business files that would need the security of opaque cardboard. However, they're excellent for home use! They're very durable and the plastic prevents the dog-ears and bending that comes with traditional cardboard-style manila folders. They came with labels that you can write on, but I just used my label maker. I had a little trouble getting the labels to stick, but I'm not sure if that was my labels or the folders. Overall, great for certain applications.
